column2: Construct an ontology focused on the following: week. Provide it in valid Turtle/RDF format, excluding any extra text.
column3: @prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .@prefix week: <http://www.example.org/week#> .week:Week rdf:type rdfs:Class .week:consistsOf rdf:type rdf:Property ;  rdfs:domain week:Week ;  rdfs:range week:Day .week:length rdf:type rdf:Property ;  rdfs:domain week:Week ;  rdfs:range xsd:integer ;  rdfs:comment "The length of the week in days"@en .week:Day rdf:type rdfs:Class ;  rdfs:subClassOf week:Week .week:Sunday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Sunday"@en .week:Monday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Monday"@en .week:Tuesday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Tuesday"@en .week:Wednesday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Wednesday"@en .week:Thursday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Thursday"@en .week:Friday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Friday"@en .week:Saturday rdf:type week:Day ;  rdfs:label "Saturday"@en .week:week1 rdf:type week:Week ;  week:consistsOf week:Sunday ;  week:consistsOf week:Monday ;  week:consistsOf week:Tuesday ;  week:consistsOf week:Wednesday ;  week:consistsOf week:Thursday ;  week:consistsOf week:Friday ;  week:consistsOf week:Saturday ;  week:length 7 .
